# Real-Time Collaborative Text Editor

This project is a real-time collaborative text editor built using **React**, **Tiptap**, **Yjs**, and **WebRTC**. It allows multiple users to edit the same document simultaneously, with user attribution and real-time synchronization.

## Features

- **Real-Time Collaboration**: Users can edit text simultaneously with others in real-time.
- **User Attribution**: Each user's edits are color-coded and displayed with their name.
- **WebRTC Integration**: Uses **Yjs** and **WebRTC** for real-time data syncing across users.

## Tech Stack

- **React**: Frontend library for building the UI.
- **Tiptap**: A rich-text editor framework.
- **Yjs**: Framework for real-time collaboration.
- **WebRTC**: Peer-to-peer communication protocol for real-time synchronization.
- **Tailwind CSS**: Utility-first CSS framework for styling.

